    "  - Behavior profiles: confirmationRequired/neutral/extendedBreakout allowed.",
    "    Blocked: falseBreakoutProne, regimeInstability, noisyHighBeta, sustainedSell.",
    "  - observeBreakoutClassifierBlocks=true: weak/first-leg breakouts suppressed even in observe mode.",
    "  - Universe policy: NEVER REMOVE symbols. The behavior-classifier profiles prevent",
    "    bad trades on weak symbols. Removing symbols is NOT the fix.",
